OL,3,CAvanti West Coast train drivers to
OL,4,Cvote on strike action in pay dispute
OL,6,FTrain drivers will ballot on whether
OL,7,Fto take strike action against Avanti
OL,8,FWest Coast in an ongoing pay dispute.
OL,10,FMembers of the Aslef union group say
OL,11,Fthe pay offer for 2026 is "not
OL,12,Facceptable".
OL,14,FThe train company runs two service
OL,15,Froutes on the West Coast Main Line
OL,16,Fbetween London Euston to Glasgow
OL,17,FCentral and Edinburgh Waverley, via
OL,18,FBirmingham New Street.
