OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782907570
OL,3,CAvanti West Coast train drivers to
OL,4,Cvote on strike action in pay dispute
OL,6,FKevin Lindsay from Aslef in Scotland,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We believed we had reached
OL,8,Fagreement with the company but they
OL,9,Ftold us they had to get approval from
OL,10,Fthe Department for Transport (DfT) and
OL,11,Fthat has not been forthcoming.
OL,13,F"Interference by the DfT in collective
OL,14,Fbargaining between the company and the
OL,15,Funion is damaging industrial relations
OL,16,Fand will make life difficult for
OL,17,Fpassengers.
OL,19,FAslef members will vote on whether to
OL,20,Ftake industrial action in the coming
OL,21,Fweeks.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
