OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782907570
OL,3,CAvanti West Coast train drivers to
OL,4,Cvote on strike action in pay dispute
OL,6,FAn Avanti West Coast spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are disappointed with the
OL,8,Fdecision by the Aslef union to ballot
OL,9,Ftheir members for industrial action
OL,10,Fover a pay offer.
OL,12,FThey added: "We remain open to working
OL,13,Fwith Aslef colleagues to resolve this
OL,14,Fdispute and will continue to try to
OL,15,Freach an agreement."
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@MOU
